---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About, Refaktor.me"
  description="Refaktor is a one-person website rebuilding service run by Steve. Years inside Apple's ecosystem, now rebuilding hobby pages, single-product sites, and family-run shops."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="top">
    <section id="about">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <div>
            <span class="tag">about</span>
            <h2>Hi, I'm <span class="grad">Steve</span>.</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="prose reveal">
            <p>Every town has one: the family restaurant where the food is perfect and the website looks like it was carved in 2010. Slow, cluttered, and impossible for the owner to update, so the lunch specials have been the same since a previous decade. Fixing it properly costs more than the ovens. That bothered me enough to do something, so I built <span class="rk">Refaktor</span>.</p>
            <p>I work every project directly, start to finish. No account managers, no handoffs, no outsourcing. You tell me what's wrong with your site, I tell you exactly what it costs and how long it takes, and I build it. The entire process fits in one email and a coffee.</p>
            <p>
              Before <span class="rk">Refaktor</span>, I spent years in sales and technical support inside Apple's ecosystem, including
              <a class="lnk lnk-istyle" href="https://istyle.ae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">iStyle<span class="idot" aria-hidden="true"></span></a>,
              an Apple Premium Reseller in Dubai and Beirut, and a stint on
              <a class="lnk lnk-apple" href="https://www.apple.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><svg class="glyph" viewBox="0 0 384 512" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M318.7 268.7c-.2-36.7 16.4-64.4 50-84.8-18.8-26.9-47.2-41.7-84.7-44.6-35.5-2.8-74.3 20.7-88.5 20.7-15 0-49.4-19.7-76.4-19.7C63.3 141.2 4 184.8 4 273.5q0 39.3 14.4 81.2c12.8 36.7 59 126.7 107.2 125.2 25.2-.6 43-17.9 75.8-17.9 31.8 0 48.3 17.9 76.4 17.9 48.6-.7 90.4-82.5 102.6-119.3-65.2-30.7-61.7-90-61.7-91.9zm-56.6-164.2c27.3-32.4 24.8-61.9 24-72.5-24.1 1.4-52 16.4-67.9 34.9-17.5 19.8-27.8 44.3-25.6 71.9 26.1 2 49.9-11.4 69.5-34.3z"/></svg>Apple</a>'s
              own Siri Machine Learning project. Standing across a counter from someone who just wants their thing to work teaches you more about design than any style guide, and it teaches you fast, because they are right there, waiting, holding the thing. You stop asking what a screen could do, and start asking what someone is trying to do at eleven at night on a phone with four percent battery.
            </p>
            <p>
              Website work isn't new to me either. I've been building and refactoring sites for my own projects for a few years, including
              <a href="https://xerolinux.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">XeroLinux.xyz</a>
              and its documentation site,
              <a href="https://wiki.xerolinux.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wiki.xerolinux.xyz</a>.
              Both still live, both still mine, both still getting quietly improved at one in the morning when I should be asleep.
            </p>
            <p>If you can't find the work you want, you build it yourself. That's <span class="rk">Refaktor</span>. You get me directly on your project, not an account manager and a support ticket, and a price that reflects one person doing the work.</p>
            <p>
              Want the longer version? It's on
              <a class="lnk lnk-linkedin" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/schaanine/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><svg class="glyph" viewBox="0 0 448 512" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M100.28 448H7.4V148.9h92.88zM53.79 108.1C24.09 108.1 0 83.5 0 53.8a53.79 53.79 0 0 1 107.58 0c0 29.7-24.1 54.3-53.79 54.3zM447.9 448h-92.68V302.4c0-34.7-.7-79.2-48.29-79.2-48.29 0-55.69 37.7-55.69 76.7V448h-92.78V148.9h89.08v40.8h1.3c12.4-23.5 42.69-48.3 87.88-48.3 94 0 111.28 61.9 111.28 142.3V448z"/></svg>LinkedIn</a>, where I stand up straight.
            </p>
          </div>

          <aside class="about-art reveal" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="globe" viewBox="0 0 440 440" fill="none" role="presentation">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="gg" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0" stop-color="#4f8cff"/>
                  <stop offset=".55" stop-color="#3fc6d8"/>
                  <stop offset="1" stop-color="#9b6cff"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <radialGradient id="sph" cx="38%" cy="32%" r="75%">
                  <stop offset="0" stop-color="#3fc6d8" stop-opacity=".16"/>
                  <stop offset=".55" stop-color="#4f8cff" stop-opacity=".06"/>
                  <stop offset="1" stop-color="#070a12" stop-opacity=".34"/>
                </radialGradient>
              </defs>

              <!-- tilted satellite orbit A -->
              <g transform="rotate(-22 220 220)">
                <ellipse class="oring" cx="220" cy="220" rx="205" ry="80"/>
                <g class="sat">
                  <animateMotion dur="30s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M15,220 a205,80 0 1,0 410,0 a205,80 0 1,0 -410,0"/>
                  <rect class="panel" x="-28" y="-5" width="15" height="10" rx="1.5"/>
                  <rect class="panel" x="13" y="-5" width="15" height="10" rx="1.5"/>
                  <line class="pl" x1="-23.5" y1="-5" x2="-23.5" y2="5"/><line class="pl" x1="-18.5" y1="-5" x2="-18.5" y2="5"/>
                  <line class="pl" x1="18.5" y1="-5" x2="18.5" y2="5"/><line class="pl" x1="23.5" y1="-5" x2="23.5" y2="5"/>
                  <line class="rod" x1="-13" y1="0" x2="-9" y2="0"/><line class="rod" x1="9" y1="0" x2="13" y2="0"/>
                  <rect class="body" x="-9" y="-7" width="18" height="14" rx="3"/>
                  <circle class="dish" cx="0" cy="-11.5" r="3.2"/>
                  <line class="rod" x1="0" y1="-8.5" x2="0" y2="-4"/>
                </g>
              </g>

              <!-- tilted satellite orbit B -->
              <g transform="rotate(28 220 220)">
                <ellipse class="oring b" cx="220" cy="220" rx="188" ry="62"/>
                <g class="sat sm">
                  <animateMotion dur="23s" repeatCount="indefinite" keyPoints="1;0" keyTimes="0;1" calcMode="linear" path="M32,220 a188,62 0 1,0 376,0 a188,62 0 1,0 -376,0"/>
                  <rect class="panel" x="-22" y="-4" width="11" height="8" rx="1.2"/>
                  <rect class="panel" x="11" y="-4" width="11" height="8" rx="1.2"/>
                  <rect class="body" x="-7" y="-5.5" width="14" height="11" rx="2.5"/>
                  <circle class="dish" cx="0" cy="-9" r="2.6"/>
                </g>
              </g>

              <!-- sphere body + wireframe -->
              <circle class="sphere" cx="220" cy="220" r="150" fill="url(#sph)"/>
              <ellipse class="spec" cx="188" cy="176" rx="52" ry="30" transform="rotate(-28 188 176)"/>
              <circle class="edge" cx="220" cy="220" r="150"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="220" rx="150" ry="30"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="162" rx="140" ry="22"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="278" rx="140" ry="22"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="114" rx="112" ry="14"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="326" rx="112" ry="14"/>
              <line class="wire" x1="220" y1="70" x2="220" y2="370"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="220" rx="108" ry="150"/>
              <ellipse class="wire" cx="220" cy="220" rx="52" ry="150"/>

              <!-- data uplink beams from the surface -->
              <path class="beam" d="M300 176 Q368 118 402 152"/>
              <path class="beam b2" d="M150 168 Q92 108 66 150"/>

              <!-- network mesh: nodes + ethernet jacks -->
              <path class="link" d="M150 168 Q224 122 300 176"/>
              <path class="link" d="M300 176 Q332 244 272 300"/>
              <path class="link" d="M272 300 Q222 336 168 300"/>
              <path class="link" d="M168 300 Q120 232 150 168"/>
              <path class="link" d="M150 168 Q224 200 272 300"/>
              <path class="link" d="M300 176 Q236 224 168 300"/>

              <circle class="ping" cx="150" cy="168" r="7"/>
              <circle class="node" cx="150" cy="168" r="5.5"/>
              <circle class="node n3" cx="272" cy="300" r="5"/>
              <circle class="node n5" cx="228" cy="222" r="3.6"/>

              <!-- RJ45 ethernet jacks as two of the nodes -->
              <g class="jack" transform="translate(300 176)">
                <rect class="jbody" x="-10" y="-8.5" width="20" height="16" rx="2.5"/>
                <rect class="jtab" x="-4" y="5.5" width="8" height="4.5" rx="1"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="-5.5" y1="-8.5" x2="-5.5" y2="-3"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="-1.8" y1="-8.5" x2="-1.8" y2="-3"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="1.8" y1="-8.5" x2="1.8" y2="-3"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="5.5" y1="-8.5" x2="5.5" y2="-3"/>
              </g>
              <g class="jack" transform="translate(168 300)">
                <rect class="jbody" x="-9" y="-7.5" width="18" height="14.5" rx="2.5"/>
                <rect class="jtab" x="-3.5" y="5" width="7" height="4" rx="1"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="-5" y1="-7.5" x2="-5" y2="-2.5"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="-1.6" y1="-7.5" x2="-1.6" y2="-2.5"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="1.6" y1="-7.5" x2="1.6" y2="-2.5"/>
                <line class="jpin" x1="5" y1="-7.5" x2="5" y2="-2.5"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-grid{display:grid;gap:2.5rem}
  @media (min-width:960px){
    .about-grid{grid-template-columns:minmax(0,62ch) 1fr;align-items:center;gap:3rem}
  }

  .prose{max-width:62ch}
  .prose p{color:var(--soft);font-size:1rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.1rem}
  .prose p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
  .prose a{font-weight:700;color:var(--soft);text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:transparent;text-underline-offset:3px;transition:color .18s var(--ease),text-decoration-color .18s var(--ease)}
  .prose a:hover{color:var(--cyan);text-decoration-color:var(--cyan)}
  /* brand-cued external links */
  .prose a.lnk:hover{text-decoration-color:currentColor}
  .prose a.lnk .glyph{height:.92em;width:auto;vertical-align:-.13em;margin-right:.16em}
  .prose a.lnk-istyle{color:var(--text)}
  .prose a.lnk-istyle .idot{display:inline-block;width:.34em;height:.34em;border-radius:50%;background:#ec1c2e;margin-left:.14em;vertical-align:.02em}
  .prose a.lnk-apple{color:var(--text)}
  .prose a.lnk-linkedin{color:#0a66c2}
  .prose a.lnk-linkedin:hover{color:#3a8ce0}

  /* wireframe globe, satellites, ethernet jacks, live data mesh */
  .about-art{display:none}
  @media (min-width:960px){.about-art{position:relative;display:grid;place-items:center;min-height:470px;transform:translateY(-2.75rem)}}
  .about-art::before{
    content:"";position:absolute;width:78%;aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:50%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(63,198,216,.16),rgba(79,140,255,.09) 46%,transparent 72%);
    filter:blur(4px);
  }
  .globe{position:relative;width:min(480px,44vw);height:auto}

  .globe .edge{stroke:url(#gg);stroke-width:2}
  .globe .wire{stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1;opacity:.2}
  .globe .spec{fill:#fff;opacity:.05}
  .globe .link{stroke:url(#gg);stroke-width:1.3;opacity:.42}

  /* nodes */
  .globe .node{fill:var(--cyan);transform-box:fill-box;transform-origin:center;animation:node-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite}
  .globe .n3{fill:var(--violet);animation-delay:1.1s}
  .globe .n5{fill:#fff;animation-delay:.7s}
  .globe .ping{fill:none;stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1.5;transform-box:fill-box;transform-origin:center;animation:node-ping 2.8s ease-out infinite}

  /* orbits + satellites */
  .globe .oring{stroke:url(#gg);stroke-width:1.4;stroke-dasharray:2 12;opacity:.42;fill:none}
  .globe .oring.b{opacity:.3;stroke-dasharray:2 10}
  .globe .body{fill:var(--panel-2);stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1.5}
  .globe .panel{fill:url(#gg);opacity:.85}
  .globe .pl{stroke:rgba(255,255,255,.4);stroke-width:.6}
  .globe .rod{stroke:var(--soft);stroke-width:1.4}
  .globe .dish{fill:none;stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1.3}

  /* ethernet jacks */
  .globe .jbody{fill:var(--panel-deep);stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1.5}
  .globe .jtab{fill:var(--panel-deep);stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1.2}
  .globe .jpin{stroke:var(--cyan);stroke-width:1;opacity:.8}

  /* data uplink beams */
  .globe .beam{stroke:url(#gg);stroke-width:1.5;stroke-dasharray:3 6;opacity:.7;animation:beam-flow 1.1s linear infinite}
  .globe .beam.b2{animation-delay:.5s}

  @keyframes node-pulse{0%,100%{opacity:.45;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.35)}}
  @keyframes node-ping{0%{transform:scale(.4);opacity:.7}75%,100%{transform:scale(1.9);opacity:0}}
  @keyframes beam-flow{to{stroke-dashoffset:-18}}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){
    .globe .node,.globe .ping,.globe .beam{animation:none}
    .globe .ping{display:none}
  }
</style>
